imap gidt <C-R>=strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M")<CR>

" gid to insert date
nmap gid a<C-R>=strftime("%Y-%m-%d")<CR><Esc>
imap gid <C-R>=strftime("%Y-%m-%d")<CR>

"Fast filetype switching
